latestPosts.caption:
is beyond excited to share with you guys the launch of my new solo video @runewpodcast on Youtube and other platforms on 12th Jan 2023 i.e. TOMORROW 

I’ve been wanting to do long format content for as long as I can remember and have even explored different formats in the past. I think i’ve finally landed on a structure that really resonates with me. 

This is going to a be a whole new side of me that you guys haven’t seen, more intimate. 

From fashion to self care, a conversation about everything and nothing. I’m a self proclaimed philosopher and I’m going to be giving and sharing with y’all my fresh perspectives on things, discussing the experiences and things we’re going through and more importantly figuring it out together. I believe at the core of human connection lies conversation, so simple yet so powerful. 

I hope you guys enjoy and love it as much as I’ve enjoyed making it. See you on the other side love you byee

Cover co directed and edited by one and only @nil0ni 
Shot by @virajdesaii
